::Battera:;

She flew towards the Allience base.  Battera carried the knowlage of 
the CF with her.  She flew as fast as she could to the allience 
base.   She flew high over the clouds and saw the sun setting on hte 
horizon.  She smiled knowing it had seemed an eternity since she saw 
the sun set.  She then thought of CyberShark.  She frowned knowing 
she might not ever see him again.  Then she shrugged, "Oh well. I'll 
survive. I have this long anyway."  She kept flying and was on a dead 
course to the base.
